1/7df1/582599_xlarge.png?m=1680677686","avatar_xxxlarge":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/5511/7df1/582599_xlarge.png?m=1680677686","created":1653406937,"last_modified":1680677686},"last_reply_by":"wonderfulcxm","last_touched":1682734111,"title":"2023.5.1,早安","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/936375","created":1682728780,"deleted":0,"content":"大家早上好！！！","content_rendered":"<p>大家早上好！！！</p>\n","last_modified":1682728780,"replies":8,"id":936375},{"node":{"avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_large.png?m=1650095340","name":"qna","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_normal.png?m=1650095340","title":"问与答","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/qna","topics":202266,"footer":"","header":"一个更好的世界需要你持续地提出好问题。","title_alternative":"Questions and Answers","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_mini.png?m=1650095340","stars":3787,"aliases":[],"root":false,"id":12,"parent_node_name":"v2ex"},"member":{"id":91323,"username":"duivan","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/duivan","website":null,"twitter":null,"psn":null,"github":null,"btc":null,"location":null,"tagline":null,"bio":null,"avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/3db37438205466ce41d61ad975b628ca?s=24&d=retro","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/3db37438205466ce41d61ad975b628ca?s=48&d=retro","avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/3db37438205466ce41d61ad975b628ca?s=73&d=retro","created":1421038967,"last_modified":1421038967},"last_reply_by":"LaurelHarmon","last_touched":1682734410,"title":"小白请教 docker","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/936385","created":1682732271,"deleted":0,"content":"本人电脑小白一个，但在网上能跟着保姆级的教程折腾一下电脑，家里软路由 esxi 虚拟了个 openwrt ，这段时间在 openwrt 中按各种教程玩起了 docker\r\n\r\n，部署了阿里云盘，alist ，TTrss ，emby 等，感觉很方便好玩，但无奈软路由内存不够（分配了给 WIN10 虚拟机一部分），有时候玩起来感觉有点慢。\r\n\r\n所以想请教大家：\r\n\r\n1. 玩 docker 最高效的方法是什么，即如果不搞虚拟机，是不是用小主机装个系统（我的理解是 debian/Ubuntu ，哪个好？），然后在这个系统中装\r\n\r\ndocker 是最高效的？\r\n\r\n2. 玩 docker ，我现在都是按网上的教程学习，把命令行 copy 运行，小白一个，所以只能一知半解，是否有专门的图形界面的软件（容器）可以管理调\r\n\r\n试参数的？ 我在群晖 nas 的就是图形界面设置那些端口，网络的。不知是不是有其他软件在 openwrt 中可以管理。\r\n\r\n3.我的群晖 220+,里面存了所有相片，非常重要，不知如果在上面玩 docker ，会不会对硬盘有影响，还是我只是玻璃心了。\r\n\r\n4. mac mini 是否可以玩 docker ，对比 win 系统玩 docker ，是更容易还是更困难？\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n上面的问题可能表达不是很专业，只是小白一个，请教了，谢谢 V2EXER!","content_rendered":"本人电脑小白一个，但在网上能跟着保姆级的教程折腾一下电脑，家里软路由 esxi 虚拟了个 openwrt ，这段时间在 openwrt 中按各种教程玩起了 docker<br /><br />，部署了阿里云盘，alist ，TTrss ，emby 等，感觉很方便好玩，但无奈软路由内存不够（分配了给 WIN10 虚拟机一部分），有时候玩起来感觉有点慢。<br /><br />所以想请教大家：<br /><br />1. 玩 docker 最高效的方法是什么，即如果不搞虚拟机，是不是用小主机装个系统（我的理解是 debian/Ubuntu ，哪个好？），然后在这个系统中装<br /><br />docker 是最高效的？<br /><br />2. 玩 docker ，我现在都是按网上的教程学习，把命令行 copy 运行，小白一个，所以只能一知半解，是否有专门的图形界面的软件（容器）可以管理调<br /><br />试参数的？ 我在群晖 nas 的就是图形界面设置那些端口，网络的。不知是不是有其他软件在 openwrt 中可以管理。<br /><br />3.我的群晖 220+,里面存了所有相片，非常重要，不知如果在上面玩 docker ，会不会对硬盘有影响，还是我只是玻璃心了。<br /><br />4. mac mini 是否可以玩 docker ，对比 win 系统玩 docker ，是更容易还是更困难？<br /><br /><br /><br />上面的问题可能表达不是很专业，只是小白一个，请教了，谢谢 V2EXER!","last_modified":1682732401,"replies":7,"id":936385},{"node":{"avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_large.png?m=1677911181","name":"programmer","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_normal.png?m=1677911181","title":"程序员","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/programmer","topics":55447,"footer":"","header":"While code monkeys are not eating bananas, they're coding.","title_alternative":"Programmer","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_mini.png?m=1677911181","stars":8357,"aliases":[],"root":false,"id":300,"parent_node_name":"computer"},"member":{"id":622036,"username":"BiQuanMe","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/BiQuanMe","website":"","twitter":null,"psn":null,"github":null,"btc":null,"location":"","tagline":"","bio":"","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/f39c13b5383fd7cb0aa20b67f6076153?s=24&d=retro","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/f39c13b5383fd7cb0aa20b67f6076153?s=48&d=retro","avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/f39c13b5383fd7cb0aa20b67f6076153?s=73&d=retro","